##How are successes distributed by insurance status?

Measure success with SSI. Variables are postop_ssi_super, postop_ssi_deep, and postop_ssi_organspace

####Setup

```{r, message = FALSE}
library(tidyverse)
```

####Clean data

Removing duplicate columns containing "flg_" and "e_", and >50% missing value. 

```{r, warning = FALSE, message = FALSE}
insurance = read_csv("./procedure10.csv") %>% 
  select(insurance_payment_type)

data = read_csv("./procedure10.csv") %>% 
  select(-starts_with("flg_"), -starts_with("e_")) %>%
  select_if(colSums(is.na(.)) < nrow(.) * 0.5)

colectomy = select(data, postop_ssi_super, postop_ssi_deep, postop_ssi_organspace)
```

```{r}
test = data %>% 
  select(insurance_payment_type)
```
